     FILES
          rz.c, crctab.c, rbsb.c, zm.c, zmodem.h Unix source files.

          rz.c, crctab.c, vrzsz.c, zm.c, zmodem.h, vmodem.h,
          vvmodem.c, VMS source files.

          /tmp/rzlog stores debugging output generated with -vv option
          (rzlog on VMS).















































